"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**CT Markets Pro User: I only know of a few other platforms that build off of BTC to maximize its security, decentralization, and popularity (Lightning, RSK, Sovryn). So why do you think there aren’t more protocols integrating with BTC?**\\n\\n**MC:** It’s the difficulty of it. It took core engineers and the Blockstack team a while to crack Proof of Transfer, making the fully expressive contract layer possible in a truly decentralized way. When you have the option of working with a restrictive and unmoving base like Bitcoin or something else (or creating your chain entirely), I think many will end up in that last bucket. It’s an easier path and with how hot crypto is, is I can assume it’s more immediately lucrative, so that’s where the focus has stayed.\",\"timestamp\":1639127903,\"title\":\"contracted by China Communications Construction Company Co Ltd\"},\"digest\":\"5MGNS_e23XUuMDx-VAXJx1bXfurfxMC3BRj01OxPSlg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x1782c973a496C4AC4e21FcF154e58DD9e60Ad4aA\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"zMpQ2kJf6yRYj-M2nIILSFaOyZz_Rlq1lu0UfgPOUYM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"4awyX8RcJCZxN4u7QwzP2i7vz4dZyajGt9qBCo7b2lA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"kNEZIFpVQ9BLAm_wGwKI_0rMIAdl1OLaMUgnoGVWJIzqOa42QoMc2HBLKZd0mQLmbOKoNWfooogHHOBEOT0AGQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4fb2e6307fec68f593c58320b387ec9eb867a24d68c70cd70e0d99814c6600dc2422c67525c16bd6d5483a015e04337aa5c7f52ba10a612426fadabd4929a2ed1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"zMpQ2kJf6yRYj-M2nIILSFaOyZz_Rlq1lu0UfgPOUYM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"4awyX8RcJCZxN4u7QwzP2i7vz4dZyajGt9qBCo7b2lA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"5MGNS_e23XUuMDx-VAXJx1bXfur